---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { CTASection } from '../components/sections/CTASection';
---

<Layout 
  title="Energy Resources & Guides | Open Energy Services" 
  description="Read our comprehensive guides on home energy efficiency, solar panels, heat pumps, insulation, and government funding in the UK."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-bg-grey min-h-[60vh]">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl text-center mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-primary-navy tracking-tighter mb-6">
        Energy Guides & Insights
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Read our comprehensive guides on home energy efficiency, solar panels, heat pumps, insulation, and navigating government funding schemes in the UK.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
        <a href="/resources/eco4-eligibility-guide" class="block bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-emerald/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-light text-emerald text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-4">Funding</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald transition-colors tracking-tight">ECO4 Eligibility Guide: Can You Get Free Insulation?</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">A complete guide to the Energy Company Obligation (ECO4) scheme, including qualifying benefits and income thresholds.</p>
          <span class="text-primary-navy font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">Read Guide &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/heat-pump-grants-uk" class="block bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-emerald/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-light text-emerald text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-4">Grants</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald transition-colors tracking-tight">Heat Pump Grants UK: The Boiler Upgrade Scheme (BUS)</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">Learn how to get £7,500 off the cost of an Air Source or Ground Source Heat Pump in England and Wales.</p>
          <span class="text-primary-navy font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">Read Guide &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <CTASection client:visible />
</Layout>